Rattrap:



Rattrap slowly awakened in the CR chamber. It was barely into full 
consciousness. His mind wasn't quite all together. He struggled to 
get up. Damage was still getting the last treatment from the systems. 
Mech fluid rounded in him again, his spark went to a healthier pulse 
and strength returned.
